Uses of Package
com.pandora.config.species.abstractions

Packages that use com.pandora.config.species.abstractions
Package
Description
com.pandora.chemistry.interfaces
This package contains interfaces related to biogeochemistry in freshwater systems, specifically focusing on PANDORA chemistry.
com.pandora.config.reactions.abstractions
This package provides abstractions for configuring and modeling chemical reactions in the context of biogeochemistry.
com.pandora.config.services
The com.pandora.config.services package provides services and interfaces related to the configuration and management of biogeochemical reactions and species in a freshwater context.
com.pandora.config.species
The com.pandora.config.species package contains classes and interfaces related to the configuration and management of biogeochemical species in the Pandora biogeochemical model.
com.pandora.config.species.abstractions
The com.pandora.config.species.abstractions package contains abstractions for representing biogeochemical species in a freshwater context.
com.pandora.config.species.services
The package com.pandora.config.species.services contains services responsible for managing the status of biogeochemical species beans.
